Package spark.api.rdf

Interface Summary
BlankNode Represents an RDF blank node, which is an anonymous resource.
Literal Represents an RDF literal value.
NamedNode Represents "named" RDF resources, most commonly represented as a URI.
PlainLiteral Represents an RDF plain literal, which has an optional language tag.
RDFNode Super-interface for all RDF node types.
Resource Super-interface for all RDF "resources".
Triple A Triple holds a subject-predicate-object triple as commonly retrieved from a CONSTRUCT query.
TypedLiteral Represents an RDF typed literal, which has a lexical representation and an XSD data type.
